WEBVTT

00:01.245 --> 00:02.280
- Hey.
- Hey.

00:02.520 --> 00:04.040
Am I interrupting something important?

00:04.041 --> 00:06.939
Impossible.
I work for the government.

00:06.942 --> 00:08.942
I just picked up the girls,
thought we'd stop by.

00:09.110 --> 00:11.427
How are the girls...

00:11.429 --> 00:12.529
Yes, they are.

00:12.531 --> 00:14.030
Hello, girls.

00:14.032 --> 00:16.733
Diane and I have been seeing
a lot of each other, recently.

00:16.735 --> 00:19.602
She is a sharp, confident, strong woman.

00:19.835 --> 00:21.402
Her children are loud.

00:23.435 --> 00:25.402
Kung fu!

00:25.403 --> 00:26.870
Here comes trouble!

00:31.076 --> 00:32.542
This is fun.

00:32.543 --> 00:33.626
Easy, girls.

00:33.628 --> 00:34.961
We'll be careful, Miss Lewis.

00:36.298 --> 00:37.430
I'm sorry.

00:37.432 --> 00:38.715
I've got it.

00:38.717 --> 00:40.016
We just wanted to invite you

00:40.018 --> 00:41.468
to come trick or treating tonight.

00:41.470 --> 00:42.886
I think I'm a little old.

00:42.888 --> 00:44.104
Can we go, Ron, please?

00:44.106 --> 00:46.473
- Please?
- You can come, sure.

00:46.475 --> 00:48.835
We have to go by 7:00 or else
the good candy will be gone.

00:48.836 --> 00:49.776
Sounds perfect.

00:50.779 --> 00:52.428
Come on, girls.

00:53.431 --> 00:54.814
Bye, guys!

00:54.816 --> 00:56.116
See you later, Ron!

00:56.118 --> 00:59.536
See you tonight!

00:59.538 --> 01:01.104
What the hell just happened?

01:02.107 --> 01:07.707
